$ %SystemDrive%\Users\Default

The `%SystemDrive%\Users\Default` directory contains *template files* (i. e. the → Windows#win-default-user-profile[default user profile]) which are duplicated when a new → Windows/user-account[user profile (account)] is created.

The exact location of this directory is stored in the → Windows/registry[registry] under
`→ Windows/registry/tree/HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE/Software/Microsoft/Windows-NT/CurrentVersion/ProfileList` in the value `Default`.
  
sa:
  → Windows/dirs/Users
